    "description": "<p>This skill only produces an effect when you have a single [One-Handed] weapon equipped to a [Hand Slot].</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Your [Attack Power] becomes [Weapon's (Attack Power) x 2]. During the first round of a scene, reduce the [Hate] cost of your [Weapon Attacks] by - 1 (minimum 0).</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>(SR 2): Instead of during the first round of a scene, you always apply the [Hate] cost reduction.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>A battle style that combines offense and defense, using one-handed weapons to attack and the other to use healing magic.</p>",
